#: ../../../source/docs/api_reference/Filesystem-API.rst:172
msgid "Setting up standard I/O devices"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/api_reference/Filesystem-API.rst:174
msgid ""
"Emscripten standard I/O works by going through the virtual ``/dev/stdin``, "
"``/dev/stdout`` and ``/dev/stderr`` devices. You can set them up using your "
"own I/O functions by calling :js:func:`FS.init`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/api_reference/Filesystem-API.rst:176
